        "Goal state decision 2026-07-07 01:48 +0800: keep the objective active. The completed pieces are UMI/Gamma code audit, datasets.bot MCP pass, and Open-X-Tactile reference review; remaining pieces are 10Kh completion, scheduler handoff to queued exact-wrist datasets, and post-training bounded conversion/validation.",
        "Scheduler guard decision 2026-07-07 01:52 +0800: do not manually start XRZero or any other queued dataset. The serial scheduler is structurally ready to start XRZero after 10Kh completion, but 10Kh is far from complete and causal_robot_daimon is still active. Note the scheduler main gate does not directly block on training processes; current practical risk is low because training ETA is much earlier than 10Kh completion, but this should be rechecked if 10Kh ever completes while training remains active.",
