            "author_type": "system",
            "kind": "comment",
            "body": "Moved from Self-Improving intro to corresponding TODO during 2026-06-24 intro cleanup:\nCollaboration update 2026-06-13: the Self-Improving working group now includes Xiaoyang from the US office plus Gao Chen, Jingxiang, Yuhang, and Li Zeyi supporting the physical-AI data / self-evolving direction. Keep the existing Tuesday 09:30-10:30 Beijing Alchedata cadence as background unless the group changes it.",
