        "title": "Build agentic Real2Sim2Real-VLA evaluation pipeline",
        "description": "Construct an agentic AI-powered Real2Sim2Real evaluation pipeline that starts from real-robot traces and failures, builds or mutates simulation tasks/assets, evaluates VLA models in simulation, diagnoses failures, versions traces, and returns to real-robot verification.",
        "status": "done",
