            "comment_id": "clawcross_b36a42a21446",
            "author": "Progress",
            "body": "## Plan\nHold the task in `blocked` while waiting on onsite physical collection by Boris/Gaochen/Jingxiang (~30 episodes each per the 2026-05-19 plan, Xiaobin observing). All dev-side enablers are done; this is purely operator-dependent now.\n\n## Execution\nHeartbeat from drag-demo-lvrobotics@100.113.210.127 on 2026-05-24. ClawCross local daemon at 127.0.0.1:51200 was unreachable from ~2026-05-23 14:xx through ~2026-05-24 (covering this Claude session's compaction window); confirmed LISTENING again on 2026-05-24, which is why this comment is the first push since the 2026-05-23T14:41 runbook update.\n\n## Modifications\nNone on the toolchain since the 2026-05-23T14:41 runbook. Files at their previous sha256s: auto_ingest.sh e75b7249f3d794966b36938d385cb5a7961c1f9a0690992a1a25949179c23e22, initial_batch_manifest.json 58b3ffb76eacfd1ba12cbd41796da82d9311d421d0001f7c3c487251d23d4ed1, raw_data_full_report.json 200c2b7669d05e123955f45623e2e9218d8b3465ffba450e8efd3f10dff487b2 (last verified during the 2026-05-23 run).\n\n## Experiments\nNo new training run today; smoke baseline from 2026-05-22T18:45 (run_id C_raw_drag_only_20260522T184538Z, final_loss 0.07975, 100 steps on RTX 4060 Ti) is the most recent reproducible evidence that the loader -> model -> backprop pipeline is end-to-end green on the 19-episode tier. Without new physical data there is nothing additional to train.\n\n## Result\nStatus unchanged: 19/100 episodes counted toward the demo_target at the accepted 0.10 rad stillness threshold (delta 81), 13 held-out for the strict eval tier at <=0.02 rad. Loader smoke passes on all 19 + 13. Operator runbook (auto_ingest.sh) is the documented one-shot to re-derive these numbers after any new collection batch lands under ~/workspace/raw_data.\n\n## Next\nESCALATION: due_at 2026-05-21 is now 3 days past as of 2026-05-24 with no onsite collection completed. Host (Boris) decision needed on (a) when the onsite operator team can run a focused collection session to land the remaining ~81 demos, or (b) whether to renegotiate the 100-demo target / due_at given the SOP yield rate observed in raw_data so far. The dev-side automation will pick up new episodes the moment they appear under ~/workspace/raw_data/<dataset>/000x/ (success) or .../_failed/f000x/ (retained failure).",
