            "comment_id": "comment_drag_demo_control_loops_20260524",
            "author": "Codex",
            "body": "Collection schema update: future drag-demo episodes should log position-loop, velocity-loop, and current-loop signals, not only RGB/depth and EEF pose. This is needed to analyze drag dynamics and contact/load response.",
            "created_at": "2026-05-24T23:47:00+08:00",
